<prosody rate="slow" pitch="-2st">
And now… it is time to bring this attunement home.
<break time="1s"/>

The Helm slows its rotation. The sphere opens, and a gentle current carries you back through the corridor. Glyphs bow as you pass—acknowledging your new calibration.
<break time="2s"/>

You stand at the hatch. Atlas hovers at the horizon of awareness, rotating polyhedron of shimmering plasma. A gentle sub-bass hum grounds you into your body here-and-now.
<break time="2s"/>

Counting up from one to ten, you return, carrying the Navigational Attunement within:
<break time="1s"/>1… feeling the surface beneath you.
<break time="1s"/>2… breath steady.
<break time="1s"/>3… limbs relaxed.
<break time="1s"/>4… awareness widening.
<break time="1s"/>5… energy integrating.
<break time="1s"/>6… clarity gathering.
<break time="1s"/>7… senses awakening.
<break time="1s"/>8… grounded and clear.
<break time="1s"/>9… eyes soft.
<break time="1s"/>10… fully present.
<break time="3s"/>
</prosody>

<!-- ================================================================ -->
<!-- SECTION 5: POST-HYPNOTIC SUGGESTIONS & ANCHORS                  -->
<!-- ================================================================ -->
<prosody rate="medium" pitch="-1st">
Each time you take three slow breaths, the Navigational Attunement reactivates, and cosmic patterns align effortlessly.
<break time="1.5s"/>

Whenever you recall the rotating polyhedron of Atlas, your intuition locks onto the clearest path ahead.
<break time="1.5s"/>

When you notice a warm hum at the base of your spine, you naturally perceive hidden meanings and synchronicities with ease.
<break time="1.5s"/>

You now carry Cosmic Pattern Recognition—the mind as a vehicle—awake, grounded, and ready.
<break time="1.5s"/>

Thank you for voyaging with Atlas, the starship of the ancient future.
<break time="2s"/>
</prosody>

</speak>